The paper focuses on the performance analysis of operations on GPUs and Many Integrated Core (MIC) architectures for a microscopy image analysis application. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Augmented Reality (cs.AR), Numerical Analysis (cs.NA), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
